  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/702790/extras/394e96ec2b5c5e818ba9fc76e4e32239.avif?t=1740235644\" width=184 height=68 /></span><br><br>This game contains two separate story lines:<br><strong>Flesh Machine</strong> and <strong>The Road to Freedom</strong><br>These two stories are in the same future background and the game system is different.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/702790/extras/e61552e8e15fded205582163491880a2.avif?t=1740235644\" width=444 height=208 /></span><br><br>Flesh Machine<br>The Flesh Machine has added moral values and focuses on the moral choice of the protagonist.<br>The end of the game will also be changed by your actions.<br>According to your own understanding and judgment of things, there are three different endings left for everyone to taste.<br>The game also added vitality values, as well as restrictions on weapons, ammunition and weights.<br>And more emphasis on survival.<br><br>The Road to Freedom<br>This story is about freedom, humanity, and he praise to people who can insist on maintaining goodness and justice even in darkness.<br>The game system of this independent story is different from \"Flesh Machine\".<br>There is no upgrade concept at all.<br>The proportion of items is stronger than that of equipment.<br>The power of weapons is not important, only focusing on pertinence.<br>The size of the enemy's volume is the key to equip with the right weapon.",
  "about_the_game": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/702790/extras/394e96ec2b5c5e818ba9fc76e4e32239.avif?t=1740235644\" width=184 height=68 /></span><br><br>This game contains two separate story lines:<br><strong>Flesh Machine</strong> and <strong>The Road to Freedom</strong><br>These two stories are in the same future background and the game system is different.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/702790/extras/e61552e8e15fded205582163491880a2.avif?t=1740235644\" width=444 height=208 /></span><br><br>Flesh Machine<br>The Flesh Machine has added moral values and focuses on the moral choice of the protagonist.<br>The end of the game will also be changed by your actions.<br>According to your own understanding and judgment of things, there are three different endings left for everyone to taste.<br>The game also added vitality values, as well as restrictions on weapons, ammunition and weights.<br>And more emphasis on survival.<br><br>The Road to Freedom<br>This story is about freedom, humanity, and he praise to people who can insist on maintaining goodness and justice even in darkness.<br>The game system of this independent story is different from \"Flesh Machine\".<br>There is no upgrade concept at all.<br>The proportion of items is stronger than that of equipment.<br>The power of weapons is not important, only focusing on pertinence.<br>The size of the enemy's volume is the key to equip with the right weapon.",
